Brian Kolfag is a veteran of the USAF, and founder of "We Build the Wall" with Steve Bannon, Kris Kobach and Eric Prince (Blackrock).

Kolfage was indicted, along with Steve Bannon and two other co-defendants, on federal charges of defrauding hundreds of donors. They raised over $9 million in three days. 

He is a triple amputee and was Arizona Rep. Gabby Gifford's guest in 2011 at Obamas inauguration. Gabby is married to current US Senator Mark Kelly from Arizona.

Funding was passed through an LLC operated by Timothy Shea of Castle Rock, Colorado.
